Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破忌者追击部队 卡拉德小队副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}还未填满绝望的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克·斯塔卡德中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉席恩·阿斯塔尔陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来处分你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有求于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如陛下之命 请你杀了莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影 现形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那肮脏的手碰蜜尔可·卡拉德一根头发试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立马杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不饶恕伤害亲人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你明白了 就眨一下眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我就放了蜜尔可·卡拉德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认她平安无事之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命掌握在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慎重小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是捡了莱纳·琉特忘记回收的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根针上可以延伸出无限的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且强韧得无法可断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到使用者的力量能使其变成如此危险的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若罗兰德以外的国家掌握了它…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说加斯塔克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你应该看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直监视他的旅途 你有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特对罗兰德 对席恩·阿斯塔尔陛下来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是必须的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人死亡 没有人哭泣的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩 这理想真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而这不过…是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直隐藏了实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开陛下 也无视寻你归国的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡去了国外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要遵守命令杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可队长会喜欢上你 也很容易理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死会令队长伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 这是我个人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人 不应该留在陛下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉 拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负基本已定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 无论如何反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两侧有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看破了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太过自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算继续活下去…我这种人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？原来你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉 脚下留情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你吃团子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为什么那个人要杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟踪我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…我来挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不像平时一样 吃掉周围的人治愈伤口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你搞不好真会被我干掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 请您…履行约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖取结晶 「噬石」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也赶快发狂变成结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人类感到绝望 悲哀的神之眼持有者们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你来拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你善良 脆弱 害怕寂寞到令人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 不是一般的快啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来几次都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太碍事了 歼灭眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 啊可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结晶化之前就杀掉了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊 竟然在放魔法途中插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那么想一个人去死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是怪物 不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你消失好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得不是我的搭档或下仆 也不是喝茶的伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你多么坚信自己是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你独自一人也不感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也无法这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是让我看了场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是童话什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后怪物就会变成人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺可喜可贺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧那家伙是怪物这事实是雷打不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怪物还是什么 我都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是活着即是祸害的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在乎世界可在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的怪物不能留活路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我管他那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他那么多…你这什么话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太随便了…这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你要是死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很寂寞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你马上就要感到寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他就要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时…一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏所有 消灭一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生 死 喜 悲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 住口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要挣扎 这就是你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论世界如何充满绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快结束这一切吧 如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放 打开 杀戮 一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到眼前的一切尽数消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到眼前的一切尽数消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会伤害人的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双血染的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法触碰任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我依然想拯救 想触及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能有所作为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了…结晶化？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉杰尔之线？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这玩意叫这个名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把你的头颅送去加斯塔克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟罗兰德找茬有什么下场…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们好好见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「噬石」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我来挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去救孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的归处 不是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉 搞什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果收获只有一个结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开所有公式者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到已经出现在罗兰德了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有…公式？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的事都不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是滑稽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说勇者还没完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来情况发生了很大变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝小姐应该快醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是轻微脑震荡 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你真的…不是普通怪物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你走后 你可知道他是什么表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为 他是真的想杀了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己背负一切 努力撑到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的王 和你们的王不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真心想创造一个人人欢笑度日的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个不折不扣的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己放下大话还这样 我还真是无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过你无可救药也不是现在才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过我觉得你们也够笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地来追我这个无可救药的窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕受伤 害怕伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才逃了出来 孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 实际上根本无法孤单下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论以为自己多么绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的是 心却还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我的力量还有用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克也有危险的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我有一件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下次我再发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直逃避自己是个怪物的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直害怕自己会杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你给我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我不再逃避 奋战至最后的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样你就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特似乎主动回归了罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 大陆各地相当数量的魔眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在集结反加斯塔克势力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以莱纳·琉特为桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成反加斯塔克战线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是今后值得考虑的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论莱纳能派上什么用场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者多么无能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本要是卢克·斯塔卡德能杀了莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对你来说反而更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会下那种命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会杀莱纳·琉特？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你是要选择最残酷的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说莱纳或许是重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为早点杀掉会比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他 马上会有代替品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为世界的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也不必牺牲朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只需走上正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的话 甚至能牺牲所有重要之人的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 爱人也都能牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你唯一的资质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再嫌麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事情有个限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这堆积如山的工作是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.87,0:23:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩你小子是魔鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 早知道还是不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德的黑暗
